tips for what every good music playing app

00:01:18.300 --> 00:01:19.300
should have.

00:01:19.300 --> 00:01:21.620
This is the music
player 'must haves.'

00:01:21.620 --> 00:01:26.450
These are the things which we're really looking
for as fundamental to what we think makes

00:01:26.450 --> 00:01:29.350
a
really good music playing experience.

00:01:29.350 --> 00:01:32.220
So the first one is it must play music.

00:01:32.220 --> 00:01:35.490
