&gt;&gt;Adam: Sounds good.

00:44:27.700 --> 00:44:28.700
&gt;&gt;Reto: And it would be relatively cheap.

00:44:28.700 --> 00:44:32.430
&gt;&gt;Adam: And if this was something that sits
