Let's--

00:44:39.020 --> 00:44:41.299
&gt;&gt;Adam: The other thing that sort of kind
of shows as well, is we have this bottom strip

00:44:41.299 --> 00:44:43.220
on each one of these pages
as well.

00:44:43.220 --> 00:44:46.869
